{"prompt": "Develop a site for an environmental advocacy group. The aesthetic should be urgent, with a chartreuse yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Environmental Urgency Now</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f0fff0; /* Very light, almost white background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #98FB98; /* Chartreuse yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n        .content h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #32CD32; /* Lime green for headings */\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            background-color: #228B22; /* Forest green for buttons */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #32CD32; /* Lime green on hover */\n        }\n        .urgency-message {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #dc143c; /* Crimson red for urgent messages */\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 2px dashed #dc143c;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.2); /* Light pinkish background for urgency */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: #98FB98; /* Chartreuse yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Our Planet is Crying Out</h1>\n            <p>Join the fight for a sustainable future. Now.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <h2>The Time to Act is Now</h2>\n            <p>We are facing unprecedented environmental challenges. Climate change, deforestation, pollution \u2013 these aren't distant threats, they are here, impacting our lives and the lives of future generations. We must move beyond complacency and embrace urgent action.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"urgency-message\">\n                The clock is ticking. Every moment of inaction brings us closer to irreversible damage.\n            </div>\n\n            <p>Our organization is dedicated to raising awareness, advocating for policy change, and implementing practical solutions. We believe in the power of collective action and the urgency of our mission.</p>\n\n            <a href=\"#donate\" class=\"cta-button\">Donate to Our Cause</a>\n            <a href=\"#volunteer\" class=\"cta-button\">Volunteer Your Time</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Environmental Urgency Now. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}